Hexen II: Hammer of Thyrion
Release Notes for version 1.4.1
===============================

Changes since HoT-1.4.1 :

Current state: 1.4.2-pre1 (pre-release, 2007-02-13)

General:
--------
- Fixed and improved parsing of puzzles.txt: This fixes the bug where the
  names used to be listed as Unknown in the puzzle pieces inventory display
  (which you can access through a key bound to the +showdm command, the
  default is q).
- Updated loading of strings.txt, infolist.txt and puzzles.txt.
- Updates to SDL input code.
- Mac OS X: Ensured that the basedir always stays the same for Mac OS X.
  (fix was added in 1.4.1-rev1).

Gameplay:
---------
- Gamecode is now at version 1.16a.
- Fixed an obscure bug where the assasin with her 4th weapon uses the tome
  of power and can't fire it. (fix was added in 1.4.1-rev1).

